In [30]:
def age_group(age):
    if age <= 20:
        return '0-20'
    elif age <= 30:
        return '21-30'
    elif age <= 40:
        return '31-40'
    elif age <= 50:
        return '41-50'
    elif age <= 60:
        return '51-60'
    elif age <= 70:
        return '61-70'
    elif age <= 80:
        return '71-80'
    else :
        return '>80'
In [31]:
df['age_group'] = df.apply(lambda x : age_group(x.age),axis=1)

def group_balance(balance):
      if balance < 0 :
        return "Bad Account"
      elif balance <72:
        return "Low Account"
      elif balance < 1421:
        return "Normal Account"    
      elif balance > 1421 :
        return "High Account"

In [52]:
def group_duration(duration):
    if duration < 300 :
        return "<5min"
    elif duration < 600 and duration >= 300:
        return "5min-10min"
    elif duration < 900 and duration >= 600:
        return "10min-15min"
    elif duration < 1200 and duration >= 900:
        return "15min-20min"
    else :
        return "from 20 minutes or more"
In [53]:
